subject: Re: Attention:Beneficiary,
body:

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm quite surprised to hear about this fund, as I don't recall being involved in any such transaction. Could you please provide more details about it? How did my name come up in relation to this fund?

I would also appreciate if you could explain the process of signing the original payment approved document. Is there a specific procedure that needs to be followed?

Looking forward to your response.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Mable
